title: Mohamed Larbi Arouri
text: Mohamed Larbi Arouri (born 13 May 1983) is a <a href="professional">professional</a> <a href="Tunisia">Tunisia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28football%29">defender</a>. His last known club was <a href="FC%20Ordabasy">FC Ordabasy</a> in the <a href="Kazakhstan%20Premier%20League">Kazakhstan Premier League</a>.
